Doug Hughes, 61, landed a gyrocopter on the West Lawn of the U.S. Capitol on Wednesday carrying 535 letters for 535 members of Congress .
He has been chaperoned back to his home in Ruskin, Florida, where he will wear an electronic tag until his first court hearing next month .
The Secret Service has decided not to prosecute Mr Hughes' wife Alena, who claims she was not aware of the plan .